Expense Tracker (MERN Stack)

A full-stack expense tracking application built using MongoDB, Express, React, Node.js, Zustand state management, JWT authentication, monthly budgets, category management, and complete CRUD operations.

Live Demo

Frontend:
https://expense-tracker-nearpay-client.onrender.com

Backend API:
https://expense-tracker-nearpay.onrender.com

------FEATURES-----

User authentication (signup, login, logout) using JWT and HttpOnly cookies

Add, edit, and delete expenses

View expenses by month and by custom date range

Search, sort, and filter expenses

Category management

Monthly budgets per category

Budget status detection (within budget / over budget)

Category colors

Responsive design

Zustand for global state management

Express-based REST API with MongoDB

-----TECH STACK-----

--Frontend--

React

Vite

Tailwind CSS

Zustand

React Router

Axios

--Backend--

Node.js

Express

MongoDB (Mongoose)

JWT

HttpOnly Cookies

CORS

dotenv

------FOLDER STRUCTURE-------

project/
│
├── client/ # React frontend
│ ├── src/
│ ├── public/
│ └── vite.config.js
│
└── server/ # Express backend
├── controllers/
├── models/
├── routes/
├── middlewares/
├── config/
└── server.js

-------Environment variables---------

-backend-

PORT=5008
MONGODB_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key
NODE_ENV=development
FRONTEND_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173

-frontend-
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5008/api

-------INSTALL DEPENDENCIES--------

Backend-
cd server
npm install

Frontend-

cd ../client
npm install

Start the backend - npm run dev
Start the frontend - npm run dev

---------API ENDPOINT--------

-Authentication-

POST /api/auth/signup

POST /api/auth/login

POST /api/auth/logout

GET /api/auth/me

-Expenses-

POST /api/expenses/addExpense

GET /api/expenses/getExpenses?month=YYYY-MM

GET /api/expenses/range?start=YYYY-MM-DD&end=YYYY-MM-DD

PUT /api/expenses/updateExpense/:id

DELETE /api/expenses/deleteExpense/:id

-Categories-

POST /api/categories/addCategory

GET /api/categories/getCategories

DELETE /api/categories/deleteCategory/:id

-Budgets-

POST /api/budgets/addBudget

GET /api/budgets/getBudgets?month=YYYY-MM

--------DEPLOYMENT-------

Deployment on Render

-Frontend (Static Site)-

Build command: npm run build

Publish directory: dist/

Production build generated by Vite

-Backend (Web Service)-

Root directory: server

Start command: node server.js

Add environment variables in Render dashboard

HttpOnly cookies enabled in production
